The Glenn Beck Radio Show JULY-01-2013 MON







The Glenn Beck Program

          
Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET

      

      
The Glenn Beck Program - 07/01/2013


Monday, July 01, 2013 10:57 AM



Glenn and the team join us from Salt Lake City,
 getting ready for Man in the Moon.

Pastor Robert Dekker discusses standing up to government's attempt to silence the gospel, 

the largest political protests in world history are going on in Egypt,

 and Adam Brandon comes in to talk about the perks of being a Gitmo detainee.
